    FinancePage --> PaymentTracking: Click Payment Tracking Tab
    FinancePage --> RevenueReports: Click Revenue Reports Tab
    FinancePage --> InvoiceAudits: Click Invoice Audits Tab
    FinancePage --> PaymentReconciliation: Click Payment Reconciliation Tab
    FinancePage --> FinancialReportsExport: Click Financial Reports Export Tab
    
    PaymentTracking --> TransactionDetails: Click View Transaction
    InvoiceAudits --> InvoiceDetails: Click View Invoice
    
    FinancePage --> GenerateCustomReport: Click Generate Report
    FinancialReportsExport --> GenerateCustomReport: Click Create Custom Report
    GenerateCustomReport --> ScheduleReport: Click Schedule Report
    
    PaymentTracking --> DiscrepancyResolution: Click Resolve Discrepancy
    InvoiceAudits --> DiscrepancyResolution: Click Resolve Discrepancy
    
    PaymentReconciliation --> MPesaImport: Click Import M-Pesa Transactions
    
    TransactionDetails --> FinancePage: Click Back
    InvoiceDetails --> FinancePage: Click Back
    GenerateCustomReport --> FinancePage: After Generate/Cancel
    ScheduleReport --> FinancePage: After Confirm/Cancel
    DiscrepancyResolution --> FinancePage: After Resolution
    MPesaImport --> PaymentReconciliation: After Import/Cancel
    
    note right of PaymentTracking
        Payment Tracking allows administrators to
        monitor all financial transactions on the
        platform, validate payments through M-Pesa
        integration, and manage any discrepancies.
    end note
    
    note right of RevenueReports
        Revenue Reports provide comprehensive analytics
        on platform revenue streams, growth trends,
        and source distribution to support strategic
        decision-making and financial planning.
    end note
    
    note left of InvoiceAudits
        Invoice Audits enable administrators to review
        all invoices generated on the platform, identify
        and resolve discrepancies, and maintain a
        detailed audit trail for compliance purposes.
    end note
    
    note left of PaymentReconciliation
        Payment Reconciliation automates the matching
        of invoices with payment records, verifies
        M-Pesa transactions, and generates reconciliation
        reports to ensure financial accuracy.
    end note
    
    note right of FinancialReportsExport
        Financial Reports Export provides tools to
        generate customized financial reports, export
        in various formats, and schedule recurring
        reports for stakeholders.
    end note
